page.title: 07Gymnastics Club
page.content: Our{Gym Club}starts at 6.30pm and finishes at 7.30pm. We meet at{Great {Houghton J.& I.School.}The teacher is called Miss Chamberlain. The cost is Â£2.50 for a full term. There are about 20 people who go. When you first join you are given a card with various tasks written on it. Miss Chamberlain asks you your name then she will give you your card and it will say on it {"Coca Cola 4".}Before you pass this card you have to be able to do a handstand and a leapfrog over a partner.From "Coca Cola 4" you can progress to{number 3.}For that you do a cartwheel and a backward roll to astride .Then you move to{"Coca Cola {2",}which is a high forward roll and a headspring.This is very difficult to do.When you reach{"Coca Cola 1"}you do an Arabspring, the splits position and a cartwheel with one hand.
